<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>Interactive Games | Renal Nursing</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #102a43;
      --blue: #176b87;
      --light-blue: #e8f4f8;
      --teal: #2a9d8f;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --text: #243b53;
      --muted: #627d98;
      --border: #d9e2ec;
      --shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(16, 42, 67, 0.12);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #f5f9fc;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .page-header {
      background:
        linear-gradient(
          rgba(16, 42, 67, 0.88),
          rgba(23, 107, 135, 0.82)
        ),
        url("images/kidney-care-banner.jpg") center/cover;
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 70px 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .page-header h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    }

    .page-header p {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .navigation {
      background: var(--navy);
      padding: 14px 24px;
    }

    .navigation a {
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .navigation a:hover {
      color: #b8edf2;
    }

    main {
      width: min(1100px, 92%);
      margin: 40px auto;
    }

    .section-heading {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .section-heading h2 {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .section-heading p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .games-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .game-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 18px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .game-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(16, 42, 67, 0.18);
    }

    .game-image {
      min-height: 190px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, #5fc3d8, transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--blue));
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 4rem;
    }

    .game-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .game-category {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--light-blue);
      color: var(--blue);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }

    .game-content h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }

    .game-content p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .play-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--teal);
      color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .play-button:hover {
      background: #21867a;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding: 24px;
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <nav class="navigation">
    <a href="index.html">← Back to Home</a>
  </nav>

  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Interactive Games</h1>

    <p>
      Explore interactive learning activities designed to strengthen
      renal nursing knowledge through clinical challenges and games.
    </p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="section-heading">
      <h2>Available Games</h2>

      <p>
        Select a game below to begin.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="games-grid">

      <article class="game-card">
        <div class="game-image" aria-hidden="true">
          🕵️
        </div>

        <div class="game-content">
          <span class="game-category">
            Renal Pharmacology
          </span>

          <h3>
            Dialysis Detective
          </h3>

          <p>
            Investigate antihypertensive medications and determine whether
            each drug is dialysable, minimally dialysable or partially
            dialysable during haemodialysis.
          </p>

          <a
            class="play-button"
            href="games/dialysis-detective.html"
          >
            Open Game
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>
      Renal Nursing Learning Hub
    </p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
